snippet.title: Mooshie's Kitchen - Indie Horror Game - No Commentary
snippet.description:
Thanks For Watching!

Facebook https://www.facebook.com/Stella-Abbasi-100150965166877/
Twitter https://twitter.com/StellaAbbasi

Download https://omogonixlachlan.itch.io/mooshies-kitchen

Welcome to Mooshie’s Kitchen! Established and operating since April 20th, 1969.

Mooshie’s Kitchen is a short, first-person mascot horror game where you play as Todd, a chef at Mooshie’s Kitchen who is finishing up his day at the establishment.

Mooshie’s Kitchen has brought joy to all walks of life since April 20th, 1969! What could go wrong?

Indie Horror Game Playlist https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLk0tZ0YT3FZEsIgd3Qdj19xGe9VcMMI1P

#MooshiesKitchen #Indiegames
